videoSnippet.title: Insane Attacking Game | Mamedyarov vs Karjakin | Norway Championship 2018 | Round 3
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Check out agadmator's chess Channel Song here https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ApkShmA65qg&t=3s

Shakhryar Mamedyarov vs Sergey Karjakin
Altibox Norway (2018), rd 3, May-30 
Italian Game: Giuoco Piano Main Line (C53)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. c3 Nf6 5. d3 d6 6. O-O h6 7. Re1 O-O 8. h3 a5 9. Nbd2 Be6 10. Bb5 Qb8 11. Nf1 Qa7 12. Re2 a4 13. Ng3 Qa5 14. Bxc6 bxc6 15. Nh4 Rfe8 16. Re1 Kh7 17. Qf3 d5 18. exd5 Bxd5 19. Qf5+ g6 20. Nxg6 fxg6 21. Qxf6 Rf8 22. Qh4 g5 23. Bxg5 Rxf2 24. Qxh6+ Kg8 25. Qg6+ Kh8 26. Qh6+ Kg8 27. Qg6+ Kh8 28. Qh6+ Kg8 29. Qg6+ Kh8 30. Qh6+
